# ── Local dev: pick ONE way to run turns ─────────────────────────────────────
#
# (1) Browser → Anthropic (simplest if you have a key; only for local dev)
#     Restart `npm run dev` after changing.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
#
# (2) Same as production: call /api/turn on your DEPLOYED Vercel app (no key in browser)
#     Set both lines; restart dev server. Your production ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is used.
# VITE_USE_API_ROUTES=true
# DEV_API_PROXY=https://your-project.vercel.app
#
# (3) Or run `vercel dev` from this folder with VITE_USE_API_ROUTES=true (uses .env.local ANTHROPIC_API_KEY on the local server).
